snippet.title: MIT Video Productions
snippet.description: As a supporting unit of the Office of Digital Learning, MIT Video Productions offers Emmy® Award-winning video production serving education, research and outreach at MIT. Working with academic programs, departments, and Institute initiatives, our experienced team understands how to communicate your message to your audience while making it clickable, accessible and sharable.
